The build quality is solid, but I worry about its longevity.
Connectivity options are improved, but compatibility issues persist. While it offers updated connectivity features, there are still some compatibility problems with certain peripherals.
Power management is efficient, but it lacks user customization. The processor optimizes power consumption effectively, but those wanting extensive control over power settings might find it lacking.
